  <div class="notice notice-type-info">
    <div class="notice-icon-area"><span class="notice-icon">&#x1F50E;</span></div>
    <div class="notice-text"><p>Pantheon is <a href="https://docs.pantheon.io/guides/global-cdn/global-cdn-beta#setup">making a change to their CDN</a>, from the legacy Pantheon GCDN (Fastly) to the new Pantheon GCDN Beta (Pantheon Cloudflare).  Before <strong>its-wws-test1</strong> can move to the new GCDN Beta, each of its custom domains must resolve through A and AAAA records instead of a CNAME record.</p>
  <p>These domains for <strong>its-wws-test1</strong> still use a CNAME record pointing at live-its-wws-test1.pantheonsite.io:</p>
  <div class="container">
  <table class="responsive-table site-updates">
